# Demo fixtures — kept in the release tarball (188 KB) because the
# v2.50–v2.62 lxc/upgrade.sh copies demo/ unconditionally.  Excluding
# it bricks every existing LXC deployment on those versions
# (cp: cannot stat '.../demo': No such file or directory → exit 1).
# The newer upgrade.sh on main no longer references demo at all and
# already guards every cp with [[ -d ]], so this can be re-introduced
# only after every LXC in the wild has updated past that script.

